The Student Legislative Council shall be deliberating on the draft of the
new Students' Constitution on the 10th of August at the Office of Hostel
Managemen Conference Room between 8pm to 10pm.

The chapters on the Rights and Responsibilities of Students shall be
discussed in this meeting. Students are welcome to join us for the same.

